{
  "stem": "27747.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Now SS and military were there. it was just an exchange of roles from a Polish army to a Russian army to a German army, except that it was-- we were in great danger from them like never before.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, my mother stayed home and she cooked for the family.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The pharmacy-- my sister worked in the pharmacy, and I helped with my-- taking care of the little cousin, my cousin's little boy.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We very seldom ventured out to the-- to the village to get food because also the villages, especially our maids, they had a lot of our belongings, our possessions.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when it came to claim them, they weren't always happy to give them back or they wouldn't give them back at all.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, when the time came in the spring, we heard rumors that they are digging graves, and the name of this small village was [POLISH].",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They wasted no time.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the rumors were true.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So my sister Leah heard that the town of [POLISH] had already an-- an action-- action-- so she figured it's safe to go there.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's about 30 kilometers from our town.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My mother and I, we were really planning to hide, but there was no special place to hide, like an attic or something like that.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were in the fields instead.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then they--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We slept out in the fields that particular night that was close already when the graves were already.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And one evening, we heard from someone that used to work with my brother in [POLISH], and he reported that tomorrow it will be the-- the action.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And go and hide and run.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And since he knew my sister, she was the one that told everyone that was able to--",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
